      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is ready for its next adventure! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
