      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats remain supple with only slight bolster wear on the driver's side, and every button, switch, and screen functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, recently receiving new brake pads and a fresh set of tires. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It\u2019s a smoke-free, pet-free environment that smells as clean as it looks. This is a reliable, attractive car that has many years of life left and is ready for its next chapter. It comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys.",
